title: the truth about being a college athlete

description:
Brooke and Danielle are joined by student athlete Brynn Chandler!  The gals talk to Brynn about being scouted, being on a team, what it’s REALLY like to be a student-athlete and so much more.  The gals also get chatty in the intro and discuss Brooke’s dating app profiles and Danielle’s senior year excitement!
